Usage: delete_ccopt_skew_groups [-help] <pattern> [-constrains <value>]
                                [-regexp]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<pattern>               # pattern for skew groups to delete (string, required)
-constrains <value>     # if specified, only deletes skew groups with the
                        # matching constrains value (string, optional)
-regexp                 # use regexp matching instead of wildcard (glob)
                        # (bool, optional)